Ep 3: Trouble in Paradise
Sam tries to bounce back after losing her listing, Chad's co-listing takes a turn, and Chad has complications.

After losing her penthouse listing, Sam heads back home to Ft. Lauderdale to help a picky buyer and her pet pit-bull find the perfect waterfront home. Chris' co-listing takes an unexpected turn that could ruin a potential deal. And while Chad is able to get a contract on his new listing in a week, an unexpected complication could cancel his premature celebration.
